            questionNumber: 3,
            questionText:
              'Read the whole extract.\n\n"The writer creates an overwhelming sense of grief through what is left unsaid. The reader feels the weight of Thomas\'s loss precisely because he does not express it directly."\n\nTo what extent do you agree with this view?\n\nYou should:\n- consider the writer\'s use of language, form, and structure\n- evaluate how the writer creates effects\n- support your views with quotations from the text.',
            marks: 12,
